name: Frida Punk 094 - FRIxDIEGO
description:
Frida Kahlo X Diego Rivera
An Artist in love with another Artist.
So much in love they married twice. There was much Frida had to say about her love of Diego.

“Diego. Truth is, so great, that I wouldn’t like to speak, or sleep, or listen, or love. To feel myself trapped, with no fear of blood, outside time and magic, within your own fear, and your great anguish, and within the very beating of your heart.” - Frida Kahlo

💎LIMITED EDITION PIECE CELEBRATING THE LOVE, LUST, ART AND LIFE OF FRIDA KAHLO & DIEGO RIVERA.
